These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, mango
The people have 2 different hobbies: drawing, skydiving
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, animation
1. the person watching superhero movies is not to the right of the person eating mango##8
2. the person eating mango is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
3. the person drinking sprite is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | sprite      |
| Food          | mango | watermelon    |
| Hobby         | skydiving   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero  | animation      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, writer
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, motorbike
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
3. the writer is not to the right of the dancer##8
4. the person driving the bike is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | fanta        | mirinda    |
| Hobby       | board-games         | rock-climbing |
| Job         | writer | dancer   |
| Transport   | bike               | motorbike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, western
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, indie
There are 2 different nationalities: british, russian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, bird
1. the british is in an odd position##4
2. the russian is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy       | western |
| Music-Genre   | reggae       | indie    |
| Nationality   | british | russian |
| Pet           | lizard        | bird   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, manager
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, italian
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway
1. the russian is somewhere to the right of the manager##5
2. the person who's hobby is baking is not to the left of the person driving the subway##8
3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | baking  |
| Job           | manager  | bartender |
| Nationality   | italian | russian   |
| Transport     | subway   | quad-bike |

